reviewText: Great and Enjoyable...must watch for all aviation enthusiasts!

I performed engine run ups flew FCF for 20 something years,  to deliver first class aircraft to the flight crews of the U.S. AIR FORCE. I WAS WELL PLEASED WITH THE DVD I RECIEVED. THANKS FOR YOUR SERVICE!

I really enjoyed it and the DVD brings back good memories. In being a former enlisted crewmember on KC-135 for nearly ten years. When I want to relive the flying and days as I crewmember; I can replay the DVD. I miss it a lot and would love to fly on the KC-135 today.
